generated_description: the pigs is an australian rock band that performs country music concerts. they have upcoming shows in sydney and newcastle, featuring country music legends such as travis collins, sara storer, paul costa, danny phegan, and pete enahy, as well as australian artists like jimmy barnes, kasey chambers, and fanny lumsden. the band has won the national folk festival infinite song contest and will be performing at the man from snowy river bush festival in corryong on april 14th. they also offer cds with free t-shirts or singles.
